274
00:13:18,730 --> 00:13:20,530
But wouldn't you feel lonely
if you were in great pain

275
00:13:20,530 --> 00:13:21,890
and those around you acted
like it's no big deal?

276
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:26,900
Like, I wonder if
I could remain calm.

277
00:13:27,370 --> 00:13:28,560
I doubt if I could.

278
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:29,800
LAUGH

279
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:31,030
Huh?

280
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:34,710
Whether you're surrounded
by people who are calm or upset,

281
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:37,610
