spend time on introductions.

321
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:45,300
I appreciate it, paparazzi.

322
00:15:47,610 --> 00:15:51,310
October 10, 2001.
Seven p.m. in Shinjuku.

323
00:15:52,250 --> 00:15:54,850
You guys all better be thankful

324
00:15:54,850 --> 00:16:00,650
for the fate of just happening to be
here right now by coincidence.

