349
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:59,370
Hey, Nobu.
Will you stop calling me Myu?

350
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,080
The name's not Myu.
It's Miu.

351
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:03,070
