no one pronounces my name properly.

354
00:18:09,850 --> 00:18:11,820
Though I really like my name.

355
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:17,690
No one does? Then I will be
the only one to call you Miu.

356
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:22,860
Are you off today?

357
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,330
Nope, we'll be on
a music show tonight,

358
00:18:25,330 --> 00:18:26,330
