him fool around with Yuri.

364
00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:43,170
Why do people easily drift
from one relationship to the next?

365
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:45,450
Until recently all he'd say was,

366
00:18:45,450 --> 00:18:47,220
