in next door to him?

383
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:44,230
That's pretty cruel.

384
00:19:46,150 --> 00:19:49,620
One reason I didn't wanna get back
with Ren is because

385
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:53,380
I was feeling Yasu's
extraordinary love for me.

386
00:19:54,290 --> 00:19:56,260
But in the end, I got swept away.

387
00:19:56,820 --> 00:19:58,550
I'm just one of the fools.

388
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,860
I'll breathe into this just to be safe.

389
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:02,790
After all, I've got important work
to do today.

390
00:20:05,630 --> 00:20:11,840
I've managed to keep on living even
when Ren wasn't around,

391
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:15,210
but without Yasu,
I'd probably fall apart.

392
00:20:17,010 --> 00:20:18,140
I've gotta end it.

393
00:20:19,180 --> 00:20:23,340
The next time I see Ren,
I won't get swept away.

394
00:20:25,750 --> 00:20:26,750
It's been a while

395
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:28,310
